      cin rexralbidv rcla4va reeanv caddc co cn0 cz nnz uzid nnnn0 syl2an fveq2
      uzaddcl eleq1d rcla4v nncn addcom ancoms eqeltrd inelcm r19.23aivv sylbir
      cc syl6 ex necon2bd syl5bi expdimp exp3a 3impd r19.23advv mpd 3exp2 imp32
      an4s necon4ad expimpd syl2ani sylbid 19.21aivv breq2 mo4 sylibr ) CUFKZBA
