  ${
    $d J m n u $.  $d X m n u $.  $d Y m n u $.
    tlmconst.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A constant sequence converges to the constant.  (Contributed by Jeff
       Madsen, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    tlmconst $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ Y e. X ) ->
                                    ( NN X. { Y } ) ( ~~>t ` J ) Y ) $=
      ( vm vu vn wcel wa cn cfv wf cv cuz wral wss c1 wceq adantll adantlr ctop
      csn cxp ctlm wbr wrex cnei w3a fconstg snssi syl11anc adantl simpr elnnuz
      fss 1nn fvconst2g ssnei biimpar syldan adantr eqeltrd sylan2br r19.21aiva
      snssg fveq2 raleqdv rcla4ev sylancr 3jca tlmbr mpbird ) AUAHZCBHZIZJCUBZU
      CZCAUDKUEJBVQLZVNEMZVQKZFMZHZEGMZNKZOZGJUFZFVPAUGKKZOZUHVOVRVNWHVNVRVMVNJ
